CNH Industrial Capital America LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 27, 2017 12:27 PM ET
Diversified Financial Services

Company Overview of CNH Industrial Capital America LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
CNH Industrial Capital America LLC provides financial services and products for agricultural and construction equipment brands in North America, Latin America, Europe, and Australia. It offers split-rate, fixed-rate, and variable-rate financing. The company also offers operating, finance, and municipal leasing services; and commercial revolving account, a credit line for day-to-day parts, service, rental, and accessory purchases. In addition, it offers physical damage insurance that provides coverage to repair or replace insured equipment in the event of direct physical loss or damage; purchased protection plans that help protect eligible new and used equipment beyond the manufacturer's base...
CNH Industrial Capital America LLC provides financial services and products for agricultural and construction equipment brands in North America, Latin America, Europe, and Australia. It offers split-rate, fixed-rate, and variable-rate financing. The company also offers operating, finance, and municipal leasing services; and commercial revolving account, a credit line for day-to-day parts, service, rental, and accessory purchases. In addition, it offers physical damage insurance that provides coverage to repair or replace insured equipment in the event of direct physical loss or damage; purchased protection plans that help protect eligible new and used equipment beyond the manufacturer's base warranty period; and credit life insurance that provides life insurance coverage to help pay off the balance due on equipment financed with CNH Industrial Capital America LLC in the event of the insured’s death. The company leases agriculture equipment that include tractors, combines, material handling equipment, hay and forage equipment, planting and tilling equipment, sprayers, commercial mowers, and attachments; and construction equipment that include excavators, backhoes/loader backhoes, wheel loaders, skid steer loaders, compact track loaders, tractor loaders, telescopic handlers, rough terrain forklifts, motor graders, dozers, compaction equipment, and attachments. The company markets retail and wholesale financing products directly to customers, and through an international network of independent dealerships and distributors. CNH Industrial Capital America LLC was formerly known as CNH Capital America LLC and changed its name to CNH Industrial Capital America LLC in February, 2014. The company was incorporated in 1993 and is based in New Holland, Pennsylvania. It has subsidiaries and joint ventures in North America, Latin America, Europe, Australia, and Asia. CNH Industrial Capital America LLC operates as a subsidiary of CNH Industrial Capital LLC.
Detailed Description


