CNH Industrial Capital LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 27, 2017 12:27 PM ET
Diversified Financial Services

Company Overview of CNH Industrial Capital LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
CNH Industrial Capital LLC is a captive finance company that underwrites and manages financing products for end-use customers and dealers of CNH Industrial America LLC and CNH Industrial Canada Ltd. in the United States and Canada. It offers retail financing products, such as retail installment sales contracts, finance leases, and operating leases to end-use customers for the purchase or lease of new and used agricultural and construction equipment, as well as provides servicing and collection operations for the retail financing products. The company also offers wholesale financing to dealers to finance purchases of new and used agricultural and construction equipment and parts, as well as e...
CNH Industrial Capital LLC is a captive finance company that underwrites and manages financing products for end-use customers and dealers of CNH Industrial America LLC and CNH Industrial Canada Ltd. in the United States and Canada. It offers retail financing products, such as retail installment sales contracts, finance leases, and operating leases to end-use customers for the purchase or lease of new and used agricultural and construction equipment, as well as provides servicing and collection operations for the retail financing products. The company also offers wholesale financing to dealers to finance purchases of new and used agricultural and construction equipment and parts, as well as extends credit to dealers for working capital and other financing needs. In addition, it provides financial products and services, including insurance and equipment protection products underwritten through a third-party insurer. CNH Industrial Capital LLC was formerly known as CNH Capital LLC and changed its name to CNH Industrial Capital LLC in February 2014. The company was incorporated in 1998 and is headquartered in Racine, Wisconsin. CNH Industrial Capital LLC operates as a subsidiary of CNH Industrial America LLC.
Detailed Description


