Get Your Equipment Today with Financing Solutions from CASE
Build and grow your business with solutions from the financing division of CASE Construction Equipment, CNH Industrial Capital. Whether it's in the field or on the job site, our construction products deliver the productivity you need for your business to succeed. 
From equipment protection plans to equipment leasing packages, CNH Industrial Capital's equipment financing products and services are designed to support you as your business grows.



















Lending

Trust the professionals at CASE to help provide unique solutions that meet your specific goals.

Discover More










Leasing

It's all about becoming more productive—and profitable. That’s what leasing can do.

Discover More




















Commercial Revolving Accounts

Productivity Plus is an exclusive line of credit designed for one purpose – to help you maximize purchasing power and productivity.

Discover More










Insurance

It's important that you protect your equipment and your business. CNH Industrial Insurance Agency provides protection products to help keep your operation running smoothly.

