CNH Industrial - Wikipedia






















 






CNH Industrial

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


CNH Industrial N.V.





Type

Naamloze vennootschap


Traded as


BIT: CNHI
NYSE: CNHI




Headquarters
London, United Kingdom[1]



Area served

Worldwide



Key people

Sergio Marchionne (Chairman)
Richard J. Tobin (CEO)


Products


Agricultural Equipment
